<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Boscolo Gift — Analisi Filtri SEO</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-primary:    #080C10;
      --bg-surface:    #0E1318;
      --bg-card:       #131A22;
      --bg-card-hover: #1A2430;
      --border:        #1E2D3D;
      --border-light:  #253444;
      --cyan:          #38BDF8;
      --cyan-dim:      #0EA5E9;
      --cyan-glow:     rgba(56,189,248,0.12);
      --cyan-glow-s:   rgba(56,189,248,0.06);
      --text-primary:  #E8EDF2;
      --text-secondary:#8A9BAC;
      --text-muted:    #4A5D6E;
      --priority-crit: #F87171;
      --priority-alta: #FACC15;
      --priority-bassa:#4ADE80;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      min-height: 100vh;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── HEADER ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0A1018 0%, var(--bg-primary) 100%);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 28px 48px 24px;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    }
    .header-inner {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .brand-icon {
      width: 42px; height: 42px;
      background: var(--cyan-glow);
      border: 1px solid var(--cyan);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-size: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px var(--cyan-glow);
    }
    .brand-text h1 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .brand-text span {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-weight: 400;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    }
    .header-meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }
    .header-meta i { color: var(--cyan); }

    /* ── MAIN ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    main {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 48px 48px 80px;
    }

    /* ── SECTION TITLE ───────────────────────────────────── */
    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .section-label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: var(--cyan);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .section-label::before {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 18px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--cyan);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }
    .section-subtitle {
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    /* ── FILTER BAR ──────────────────────────────────────── */
    .filter-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .filter-bar-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .filter-btn {
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg-card);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    .filter-btn:hover {
      border-color: var(--cyan-dim);
      color: var(--cyan);
      background: var(--cyan-glow-s);
    }
    .filter-btn.active {
      border-color: var(--cyan);
      color: var(--cyan);
      background: var(--cyan-glow);
    }
    .pill-critica  { background: rgba(248,113,113,0.12); color: #F87171; border-color: rgba(248,113,113,0.3); }
    .pill-alta     { background: rgba(250,204,21,0.10);  color: #FACC15; border-color: rgba(250,204,21,0.3);  }
    .pill-bassa    { background: rgba(74,222,128,0.10);  color: #4ADE80; border-color: rgba(74,222,128,0.3);  }

    /* ── CARDS GRID ──────────────────────────────────────── */
    .cards-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(380px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 24px 24px 20px;
      transition: all 0.25s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: transparent;
      transition: background 0.25s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      background: var(--bg-card-hover);
      border-color: var(--border-light);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), 0 0 0 1px var(--border-light);
    }
    .card:hover::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), transparent);
    }
    .card.hidden { display: none; }

    .card-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .card-id {
      width: 30px; height: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--cyan-glow);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.3);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--cyan);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .card-title {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      flex: 1;
    }
    .priority-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.67rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .priority-badge.CRITICA {
      background: rgba(248,113,113,0.15);
      color: var(--priority-crit);
      border: 1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.3);
    }
    .priority-badge.ALTA {
      background: rgba(250,204,21,0.12);
      color: var(--priority-alta);
      border: 1px solid rgba(250,204,21,0.3);
    }
    .priority-badge.BASSA {
      background: rgba(74,222,128,0.10);
      color: var(--priority-bassa);
      border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.3);
    }

    .card-meta-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .meta-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      padding: 3px 9px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .meta-tag i { color: var(--cyan); font-size: 0.68rem; }

    .card-values {
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .card-values-label {
      font-size: 0.67rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
    }
    .values-chips {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .value-chip {
      padding: 3px 9px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: rgba(56,189,248,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.15);
      font-size: 0.73rem;
      color: #90CAF9;
    }

    .card-motivation {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
      border-left: 2px solid var(--cyan);
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .card-motivation-label {
      font-size: 0.67rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
    }

    /* ── DIVIDER ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .section-divider {
      margin: 64px 0 48px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .section-divider::before,
    .section-divider::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
    }
    .section-divider-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      background: var(--bg-surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* ── IMPROVE TABLE ───────────────────────────────────── */
    .table-wrapper {
      overflow-x: auto;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 0.84rem;
    }
    thead tr {
      background: var(--bg-surface);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    thead th {
      padding: 14px 20px;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    thead th i {
      margin-right: 7px;
      color: var(--cyan);
    }
    tbody tr {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background 0.18s;
    }
    tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    tbody tr:hover { background: var(--bg-card-hover); }
    tbody tr.hidden { display: none; }
    tbody td {
      padding: 18px 20px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      vertical-align: top;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    tbody td:first-child {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .td-stato {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .td-problem {
      color: #E8A0A0;
      font-size: 0.81rem;
    }
    .td-solution {
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-size: 0.81rem;
    }

    /* ── STATS ROW ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    .stats-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .stat-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 20px 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .stat-value {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--cyan);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .stat-icon {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    /* ── SEARCH ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .search-input-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 200px;
      max-width: 320px;
    }
    .search-input-wrapper i {
      position: absolute;
      left: 12px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .search-input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 7px 14px 7px 34px;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
      outline: none;
    }
    .search-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .search-input:focus { border-color: var(--cyan-dim); }

    /* ── EMPTY STATE ─────────────────────────────────────── */
    .empty-state {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      display: none;
    }
    .empty-state i { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--border-light); }
    .empty-state p { font-size: 0.875rem; }

    /* ── FOOTER ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 24px 48px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }
    footer span { color: var(--cyan); }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ──────────────────────────────────────── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header { padding: 20px 24px; }
      main   { padding: 32px 24px 60px; }
      .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .section-title { font-size: 1.3rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ HEADER -->
<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="brand-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i></div>
      <div class="brand-text">
        <h1>Boscolo Gift</h1>
        <span>SEO Filter Analysis</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <i class="fa-regular fa-calendar"></i>
      Analisi Filtri E-commerce &nbsp;·&nbsp;
      <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i>
      Report SEO
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ MAIN -->
<main>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <div class="stats-row">
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus-circle"></i></div>
      <div class="stat-value">6</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Nuovi Filtri</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-wrench"></i></div>
      <div class="stat-value">3</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Filtri da Migliorare</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-fire"></i></div>
      <div class="stat-value">2</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Priorità Critica</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-trend-up"></i></div>
      <div class="stat-value">4</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Priorità Alta</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-leaf"></i></div>
      <div class="stat-value">2</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Priorità Bassa</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── SEZIONE 1: NUOVI FILTRI ─────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-sparkles"></i> Sezione 1</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Nuovi Filtri Raccomandati</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Filtri non ancora presenti nel sito, raccomandati per migliorare l'esperienza utente e la performance SEO.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Filter bar sezione 1 -->
  <div class="filter-bar" id="filterBar1">
    <div class="filter-bar-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-sliders"></i> Filtra per priorità</div>
    <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all" data-target="new">Tutti</button>
    <button class="filter-btn pill-critica" data-filter="CRITICA" data-target="new">Critica</button>
    <button class="filter-btn pill-alta" data-filter="ALTA" data-target="new">Alta</button>
    <button class="filter-btn pill-bassa" data-filter="BASSA" data-target="new">Bassa</button>
    <div class="search-input-wrapper">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
      <input class="search-input" type="text" placeholder="Cerca filtro..." id="searchNew" oninput="searchCards('new', this.value)"/>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Cards nuovi filtri -->
  <div class="cards-grid" id="cardsNew">

    <!-- Card 1 -->
    <div class="card" data-priority="CRITICA">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="card-id">01</div>
        <div class="card-title">Per Chi è il Regalo</div>
        <div class="priority-badge CRITICA"><i class="fa-solid fa-fire"></i>Critica</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-meta-row">
        <span class="meta-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-list-check"></i> Multi-select checkbox</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-values">
        <div class="card-values-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i> Valori Suggeriti</div>
        <div class="values-chips">
          <span class="value-chip">Per Lei</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Per Lui</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Per la Coppia</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Per la Famiglia</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Per i Bambini</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Per i Nonni</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Per il Collega</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-motivation">
        <div class="card-motivation-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i> Motivazione</div>
        Permette personalizzazione immediata. Riduce la navigazione irrilevante. Alta risonanza emotiva.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2 -->
    <div class="card" data-priority="ALTA">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="card-id">02</div>
        <div class="card-title">Valutazione / Rating</div>
        <div class="priority-badge ALTA"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up"></i>Alta</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-meta-row">
        <span class="meta-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i> Stelle checkbox</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-values">
        <div class="card-values-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i> Valori Suggeriti</div>
        <div class="values-chips">
          <span class="value-chip">5 stelle</span>
          <span class="value-chip">4+ stelle</span>
          <span class="value-chip">3+ stelle</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-motivation">
        <div class="card-motivation-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i> Motivazione</div>
        Aumenta fiducia e riduce incertezza. Solo Virgin lo ha — filtro differenziante. Richiede sistema recensioni attivo (prospettiva futura).
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3 -->
    <div class="card" data-priority="ALTA">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="card-id">03</div>
        <div class="card-title">Quality</div>
        <div class="priority-badge ALTA"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up"></i>Alta</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-meta-row">
        <span class="meta-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i> Multi-select o dropdown</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-values">
        <div class="card-values-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i> Valori Suggeriti</div>
        <div class="values-chips">
          <span class="value-chip">Premium</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Lusso</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Ultra-Luxury</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-motivation">
        <div class="card-motivation-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i> Motivazione</div>
        Segmenta il catalogo per capacità di spesa. Target alto-spendente in crescita. Boscolo ha heritage nel luxury.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 4 -->
    <div class="card" data-priority="BASSA">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="card-id">04</div>
        <div class="card-title">Sostenibilità / Eco</div>
        <div class="priority-badge BASSA"><i class="fa-solid fa-leaf"></i>Bassa</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-meta-row">
        <span class="meta-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-toggle-on"></i> Toggle</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-values">
        <div class="card-values-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i> Valori Suggeriti</div>
        <div class="values-chips">
          <span class="value-chip">Solo esperienze eco-sostenibili</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-motivation">
        <div class="card-motivation-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i> Motivazione</div>
        Nicchia in crescita.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 5 -->
    <div class="card" data-priority="BASSA">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="card-id">05</div>
        <div class="card-title">Feature Speciali</div>
        <div class="priority-badge BASSA"><i class="fa-solid fa-leaf"></i>Bassa</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-meta-row">
        <span class="meta-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-list-check"></i> Multi-select checkbox</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-values">
        <div class="card-values-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i> Valori Suggeriti</div>
        <div class="values-chips">
          <span class="value-chip">Pet-Friendly</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Accessibile</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Family-Friendly</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Parcheggio incluso</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Raggiungibile in treno</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-motivation">
        <div class="card-motivation-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i> Motivazione</div>
        Nicchia ad alto valore. Chi cerca esperienze accessibili trova raramente filtri dedicati.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 6 -->
    <div class="card" data-priority="ALTA">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="card-id">06</div>
        <div class="card-title">Destinazione Unificata</div>
        <div class="priority-badge ALTA"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up"></i>Alta</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-meta-row">
        <span class="meta-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass-location"></i> Search box + filtro geografico</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-values">
        <div class="card-values-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i> Valori Suggeriti</div>
        <div class="values-chips">
          <span class="value-chip">Cerca città o regione</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Vicino a me (GPS)</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Nord Italia</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Centro Italia</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Sud Italia</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Europa</span>
          <span class="value-chip">Mondo</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-motivation">
        <div class="card-motivation-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i> Motivazione</div>
        Sostituisce i 3 filtri separati (Paese + Regione + Provincia) con un'unica UX pulita e mobile-first.
      </div>
    </div>

  </div><!-- /cards-grid -->
  <div class="empty-state" id="emptyNew"><i class="fa-solid fa-filter-circle-xmark"></i><p>Nessun filtro corrisponde alla selezione.</p></div>

  <!-- ─── DIVIDER ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="section-divider">
    <div class="section-divider-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-wrench"></i></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── SEZIONE 2: FILTRI DA MIGLIORARE ──────────────────── -->
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-pen-to-square"></i> Sezione 2</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Filtri da Migliorare</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Filtri già presenti ma con problemi di UX, struttura o logica SEO che ne limitano l'efficacia.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Filter bar sezione 2 -->
  <div class="filter-bar" id="filterBar2">
    <div class="filter-bar-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-sliders"></i> Filtra per priorità</div>
    <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all" data-target="improve">Tutti</button>
    <button class="filter-btn pill-critica" data-filter="CRITICA" data-target="improve">Critica</button>
    <button class="filter-btn pill-alta" data-filter="ALTA" data-target="improve">Alta</button>
    <div class="search-input-wrapper">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
      <input class="search-input" type="text" placeholder="Cerca filtro..." id="searchImprove" oninput="searchRows('improve', this.value)"/>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Table filtri da migliorare -->
  <div class="table-wrapper">
    <table id="tableImprove">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th><i class="fa-solid fa-filter"></i>Filtro</th>
          <th><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i>Stato Attuale</th>
          <th><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>Problema</th>
          <th><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i>Soluzione Raccomandata</th>
          <th><i class="fa-solid fa-signal"></i>Priorità</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>

        <tr data-priority="ALTA">
          <td>Prezzo</td>
          <td class="td-stato">Slider lineare min-max</td>
          <td class="td-problem">Su mobile lo slider è difficile da usare con precisione. Non mostra le fasce di valore. Mancano contatori per fascia.</td>
          <td class="td-solution">Affiancare allo slider 5 bottoni preset: [&lt; 50 EUR] [50–100 EUR] [100–200 EUR] [200–300 EUR] [&gt; 300 EUR]. Ogni bottone mostra il numero di prodotti.</td>
          <td><span class="priority-badge ALTA"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up"></i>Alta</span></td>
        </tr>

        <tr data-priority="CRITICA">
          <td>Tema → Categoria + Occasione</td>
          <td class="td-stato">Lista checkbox mista (temi + occasioni)</td>
          <td class="td-problem">Mescola natura diversa dei filtri: "Momenti Speciali" è un'occasione, "Benessere" è una categoria. Si potrebbe aggiungere anche "Esperienze romantiche".</td>
          <td class="td-solution">Separare in 2 filtri distinti:<br><br><strong style="color:#E8EDF2">1. CATEGORIA ESPERIENZA:</strong> Benessere, Gastronomia, Avventura, Soggiorno, Cultura<br><br><strong style="color:#E8EDF2">2. OCCASIONE:</strong> Momenti romantici, momenti in famiglia… etc.</td>
          <td><span class="priority-badge CRITICA"><i class="fa-solid fa-fire"></i>Critica</span></td>
        </tr>

        <tr data-priority="ALTA">
          <td>Paese + Regione + Provincia</td>
          <td class="td-stato">3 filtri separati indipendenti</td>
          <td class="td-problem">3 filtri geografici indipendenti creano confusione, occupano troppo spazio nel sidebar, hanno logica di selezione non chiara.</td>
          <td class="td-solution">Sostituire con un unico filtro "Destinazione": [Cerca per città, regione o paese…] + quick-select: [Vicino a me] [Italia] [Europa] [Mondo].</td>
          <td><span class="priority-badge ALTA"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up"></i>Alta</span></td>
        </tr>

      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <div class="empty-state" id="emptyImprove"><i class="fa-solid fa-filter-circle-xmark"></i><p>Nessun filtro corrisponde alla selezione.</p></div>

</main>

